## 4. User Roles & Permissions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The system uses a **single Admin role** (unified) instead of separate Super Admin and Operations Admin.

### 4.1 Admin (Unified)

| Area | Permissions |
|------|------------|
| Users | Add, edit, deactivate all users |
| Guards | Full CRUD, assign to sites, manage documents |
| Sites | Full CRUD, configure geo-fence, assign guards |
| Attendance | View all, edit/correct, generate reports |
| Payroll | Generate, approve, view all salary slips |
| Recruitment | Full access to candidate pipeline |
| Inspections | View all reports, assign inspections |
| Settings | App configuration, shift timings, geo-fence radius |
| Reports | Generate and export all reports |

### 4.2 Manager / Inspector

| Area | Permissions |
|------|------------|
| Sites | View assigned sites only |
| Inspections | Create reports, upload photos, submit remarks |
| Guards | Verify presence at assigned sites |
| Incidents | Report and document incidents |
| **Restrictions** | No payroll, no recruitment, no user management |

### 4.3 Recruiter / Telecaller

| Area | Permissions |
|------|------------|
| Candidates | Full CRUD on candidate records |
| Pipeline | Filter, contact, update candidate status |
| **Restrictions** | No payroll, no attendance, no site management |

### 4.4 Security Guard

| Area | Permissions |
|------|------------|
| Attendance | Mark check-in / check-out (own only) |
| Profile | View own profile, documents |
| Salary | View own salary slips |
| Shifts | View assigned shift details |
| Reports | Upload incident reports |

