## 5. Functional Requirements

### 5.1 Authentication Module (FR-AUTH)

| ID | Requirement |
|----|------------|
| FR-AUTH-01 | Mobile OTP login via Firebase Authentication |
| FR-AUTH-02 | JWT-based session with refresh tokens |
| FR-AUTH-03 | Role-based routing after login |
| FR-AUTH-04 | Auto-logout on token expiry |
| FR-AUTH-05 | Device-based login validation (optional) |

**Inputs:** Mobile number, OTP  
**Outputs:** JWT token, user session, role-based navigation

### 5.2 Guard Management (FR-GUARD)

| ID | Requirement |
|----|------------|
| FR-GUARD-01 | Add new guard with full profile |
| FR-GUARD-02 | Edit guard details |
| FR-GUARD-03 | Upload documents (Aadhaar, PAN, photo, police verification) |
| FR-GUARD-04 | Assign guard to site with shift type |
| FR-GUARD-05 | Track employment status (Active / Inactive / Terminated) |
| FR-GUARD-06 | View guard history (sites, attendance, salary) |

**Guard Profile Fields:**
Name, Phone, Aadhaar Number, PAN, Address, Photo, Height, Weight, Education, Police Verification Status, Base Salary, Uniform Status, Joining Date, Shift Type (Day/Night/Rotational), Emergency Contact, Bank Details

### 5.3 Site Management (FR-SITE)

| ID | Requirement |
|----|------------|
| FR-SITE-01 | Add client site with GPS coordinates |
| FR-SITE-02 | Configure geo-fence radius (default 100m, configurable) |
| FR-SITE-03 | Configure shift timings per site |
| FR-SITE-04 | Assign guards (day shift + night shift) |
| FR-SITE-05 | Track active guard count per site |
| FR-SITE-06 | Site status (Active / Inactive) |

**Site Fields:**
Site Name, Client Name, Address, Latitude, Longitude, Geo-fence Radius, Day Shift Timing, Night Shift Timing, Day Guards Count, Night Guards Count, Contact Person, Contact Phone

### 5.4 Attendance System (FR-ATT)

| ID | Requirement |
|----|------------|
| FR-ATT-01 | GPS validation — guard must be within geo-fence |
| FR-ATT-02 | Selfie capture at check-in and check-out |
| FR-ATT-03 | Shift timing validation (±30 min tolerance) |
| FR-ATT-04 | Prevent duplicate check-in for same shift |
| FR-ATT-05 | Attendance history with filters (date, guard, site) |
| FR-ATT-06 | Admin can manually correct attendance |
| FR-ATT-07 | Late arrival / early departure flagging |

**Attendance Flow:**
```
Guard opens app → Attendance screen → GPS check → Within geo-fence?
  → YES → Capture selfie → Validate shift timing → Submit → Store in DB → Notify Admin
  → NO → Show error "You are not at your assigned site"
```

### 5.5 Payroll Management (FR-PAY)

| ID | Requirement |
|----|------------|
| FR-PAY-01 | Auto-calculate salary based on attendance |
| FR-PAY-02 | Apply overtime (hours beyond shift) |
| FR-PAY-03 | Apply penalty deductions (absences, late) |
| FR-PAY-04 | Apply uniform deductions |
| FR-PAY-05 | Apply advance salary deductions |
| FR-PAY-06 | Generate monthly salary slips |
| FR-PAY-07 | Guard can view own salary slips |

**Salary Formula:**
```
Final Salary = (Base Salary / Total Working Days) × Days Present
             + Overtime Amount
             - Penalty Deductions
             - Uniform Dues
             - Advance Deductions
```

### 5.6 Uniform Management (FR-UNI)

| ID | Requirement |
|----|------------|
| FR-UNI-01 | Track uniform items issued to each guard |
| FR-UNI-02 | Track payment status per item |
| FR-UNI-03 | Auto-deduct from salary if configured |

**Items:** Uniform Set, Shoes, Belt, Cap, ID Card, Torch, Baton, Whistle

### 5.7 Recruitment Management (FR-REC)

