## 8. API Architecture

### 8.1 Authentication
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/auth/send-otp` | Send OTP to mobile |
| POST | `/auth/verify-otp` | Verify OTP, return JWT |
| POST | `/auth/refresh` | Refresh token |
| POST | `/auth/logout` | Invalidate session |

### 8.2 Guards
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/guards` | List all guards (Admin) |
| POST | `/guards` | Add new guard |
| GET | `/guards/:id` | Guard details |
| PUT | `/guards/:id` | Update guard |
| POST | `/guards/:id/documents` | Upload documents |
| POST | `/guards/:id/assign-site` | Assign to site |

### 8.3 Sites
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/sites` | List all sites |
| POST | `/sites` | Create site |
| GET | `/sites/:id` | Site details with assigned guards |
| PUT | `/sites/:id` | Update site |

### 8.4 Attendance
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/attendance/check-in` | Submit check-in |
| POST | `/attendance/check-out` | Submit check-out |
| GET | `/attendance/history` | Filtered history |
| GET | `/attendance/daily-summary` | Today's summary |
| PUT | `/attendance/:id` | Manual correction (Admin) |

### 8.5 Payroll
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/payroll/generate` | Generate monthly payroll |
| GET | `/payroll/slips` | List salary slips |
| GET | `/payroll/slips/:id` | Slip details |
| PUT | `/payroll/slips/:id/approve` | Approve payroll |

### 8.6 Recruitment
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/candidates` | Add candidate |
| GET | `/candidates` | Filter candidates |
| PUT | `/candidates/:id` | Update candidate |
| POST | `/candidates/:id/convert` | Convert to guard |

### 8.7 Inspections
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/inspections` | Submit inspection |
| GET | `/inspections` | List inspections |
| GET | `/inspections/:id` | Inspection details |

